    "title": "What plaything can you offer me today?",
    "description": "Moxxi weapon: while held, heals you for 3% of all damage you deal. +200% critical hit damage (scaled). Fires arcing bullets that split into two after a set distance. Rounds explode on impact, dealing splash damage equal to 80% of weapon damage; this splash is affected by grenade damage bonuses."
